  "slug": "codex-overview",
  "title": "Codex 适合做什么",
  "description": "理解 Codex 在 Anydocs 工作流中的角色。",
  "tags": [
    "codex",
    "overview"
  ],
  "status": "published",
  "updatedAt": "2026-03-19T00:00:00.000Z",
  "content": {
    "version": 1,
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "id": "block-1",
        "level": 1,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Codex 适合做什么"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Codex 更适合承担“有明确工具边界和结果产物”的工作，而不是自由发挥地改一堆 JSON 文件。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-3",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "在 Anydocs 场景里，最适合交给 Codex 的任务包括："
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "id": "block-4",
        "style": "bulleted",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "element-4-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "检查项目 contract 和语言配置"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-5-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "按页面 ID / slug 查找现有内容"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-6-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "新建文档页、更新文档页、推进页面状态"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-7-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "在改动前后读取导航与页面状态做确认"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-8",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "最关键的原则是：**让 Codex 调用 MCP 工具，而不是猜测文件结构后直接落盘。**"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
